==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Noted
<hw>Not"ed</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>a.</pos> <def>Well known by
reputation or report; eminent; famous; prominent; celebrated; <as>as, a
<ex>noted</ex> author, or traveler</as>.</def> --
<wordforms><wf>Not"ed*ly</wf>, <pos>adv.</pos> -- <wf>Not"ed*ness</wf>,
<pos>n.</pos></wordforms>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Noteful</ent>⟦br⟧
